title: Bobby Spent His Weekend In The Wild With Bear Grylls + Producer Eddie Gets Accused of Stealing
itunes:title: Bobby Spent His Weekend In The Wild With Bear Grylls + Producer Eddie Gets Accused of Stealing
description:
Bobby flew out of the country over the weekend to film an episode of “Running Wild” with Bear Grylls. Lunchbox guesses listeners’ weights just by talking to them over the phone. Also, Eddie gets accused of stealing when trying to return a gift.
